SAA to Introduce Flights to Nigeria, Congo, Burundi, Business Report Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-10T05:20:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/saa-to-introduce-flights-to-nigeria-congo-burundi-business-report-says.html
South African Airways  plans to add
flights to Abuja in  Nigeria , Madagascar, the Republic of Congo
and Burundi while growing in  South America ,  Asia  and  India ,
Johannesburg-based  Business Report  said, citing Chief Executive
Officer Siza Mzimela.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  